comment:
* An exception thrown when an error encountered during migration.
 *
 * @hide

variables.name: ERROR_INTERNAL
variables.comment: An internal error occurred during migration. Retrying should resolve the problem.

variables.name: ERROR_MIGRATE_ENTITY
variables.comment:
* An error occurred during migration of an entity, {@link #getFailedEntityId()} is guaranteed
     * to be not null.

variables.name: ERROR_MIGRATION_UNAVAILABLE
variables.comment:
* Indicates that the module does not accept migration data anymore, the caller should stop the
     * migration process altogether.

methods.name: public String getFailedEntityId()
methods.comment:
* Returns an optional id of the first failed entity, populated when the error code is {@link
     * MigrationException#ERROR_MIGRATE_ENTITY}.

methods.name: public void writeToParcel(@NonNull Parcel dest, int flags)

methodNames: public void writeToParcel(@NonNull Parcel dest, int flags)
